              <a class="keyword-chip" href="#what">Newcomer OESP eligibility</a>
              <a class="keyword-chip" href="#what">Hydro bill help Toronto</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection
      title="Toronto household budget feeling tight?"
      body="OESP is the easiest 15 minutes you'll spend this year. If you know a senior, a tenant, a newcomer family, or a young household whose hydro bill is over $100/month, send them this article — or send me a quick note and I'll walk them through it."
      ctaPrimary={{ href: '/contact', label: 'Get in touch' }}
      ctaSecondary={{ href: '/blog', label: 'More Toronto guides' }}
    />
  </article>

